---
import { t } from "i18next";
import { Trans } from "astro-i18next/components";
---

<!-- note: next time use CSS grid directly, don't mess around with relative positions -->
<div class="sm:pb-8 md:pb-4 lg:pb-12">
  <div
    class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-7xl lg:px-8 lg:bg-transparent bg-contentbackground"
  >
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12">
      <div
        class="z-10 lg:col-span-4 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-1 lg:py-16 lg:bg-transparent"
      >
        <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-xs sm:px-6 md:max-w-md lg:p-0">
          <img
            decoding="async"
            loading="lazy"
            class="object-cover object-center w-full max-w-md rounded-3xl shadow-2xl -rotate-2 "
            src="/images/about.webp"
            alt={t("about.img1")}
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative rounded-3xl lg:grid lg:grid-cols-10 lg:col-span-10 lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-1 lg:items-center lg:bg-contentbackground"
      >
        <div
          class="hidden overflow-hidden absolute inset-0 rounded-3xl pointer-events-none lg:block"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <svg
            class="absolute bottom-full left-full opacity-20 transform -translate-x-2/3 translate-y-1/3 xl:top-0 xl:bottom-auto xl:translate-y-0"
            width="404"
            height="384"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 404 384"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <defs>
              <pattern
                id="64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
              >
                <rect
                  x="0"
                  y="0"
                  width="4"
                  height="4"
                  class="text-accent-500"
                  fill="currentColor"></rect>
              </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect
              width="404"
              height="384"
              fill="url(#64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d)"></rect>
          </svg>
          <svg
            class="absolute top-full opacity-40 transform -translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/3 xl:-translate-y-1/2"
            width="404"
            height="384"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 404 384"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <defs>
              <pattern
                id="64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
              >
                <rect
                  x="0"
                  y="0"
                  width="4"
                  height="4"
                  class="text-accent-500"
                  fill="currentColor"></rect>
              </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect
              width="404"
              height="384"
              fill="url(#64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d)"></rect>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div
          class="py-12 mx-auto space-y-6 sm:py-16 sm:max-w-3xl lg:col-span-7 lg:col-start-4 lg:max-w-none"
        >
          <h2
            class="text-4xl font-semibold sm:text-5xl"
            id="about-heading"
          >
            <Trans i18nKey="about.heading1">
              I am <strong>Eric Trigo</strong>, a <strong>freelance dev</strong> mainly focused on <strong>.NET</strong>, <strong>containers</strong> and <strong>the cloud</strong>.
            </Trans>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-primary-300 md:text-primary-100 text-justify">
            <Trans i18nKey="about.body1">
              I've never known life without computers, for better or worse. I learned how to code very early in my life, thanks to <a
                rel="prefetch"
                target="_blank"
                href="http://www.vicentetrigo.com"
                class="hover:decoration-accent-300 font-semibold hover:text-accent-400 active:text-accent-400"
              >my dad</a> and <a
                rel="prefetch"
                target="_blank"
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/isaac-trigo-conde-7774932/"
                class="hover:decoration-accent-300 font-semibold hover:text-accent-400 active:text-accent-400"
              >brother</a>.
              <br />
              <br />
              Although I've spent most of my career doing backend development based around the .NET ecosystem, these days you're more likely to find me fixing a broken CI/CD pipeline or deploying containers to a Kubernetes cluster.
            </Trans>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="mx-auto space-y-6 sm:py-16 sm:max-w-3xl lg:col-span-7 lg:col-start-4 lg:max-w-none"
  >
    <h2
      class="text-3xl font-semibold sm:text-4xl"
      id="about-heading"
    >
      <img
        decoding="async"
        loading="lazy"
        class="object-fill rounded-3xl shadow-2xl mb-10"
        src="/images/pilar.webp"
        alt={t("about.img2")}
      />
      <Trans i18nKey="about.heading2">
        I live in <a
          rel="prefetch"
          target="_blank"
          href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zaragoza"
          class="hover:decoration-accent-300 font-semibold hover:text-accent-400 active:text-accent-400"
        ><strong>Saragossa, Spain</strong></a>, from where I work <strong>remotely</strong>.
      </Trans>
    </h2>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-primary-300 md:text-primary-100">
      <Trans i18nKey="about.body21">
        <strong>Music</strong> is one of my biggest passions, which I inherited from my dad.
        <br />
        <br />
        These songs put me in a good mood. I hope you like them! &#128515;
      </Trans>
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap">
      <div class="w-1/2 p-4">
        <iframe style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/7jIAttgQTpLDoNtykIQXjH?utm_source=generator" width="100%" height="152" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="w-1/2 p-4">
        <iframe style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/1mU2HQ7eS6KTvbXYUVfyFO?utm_source=generator" width="100%" height="152" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap">
      <div class="w-1/2 p-4">
        <iframe style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/3jBCYko1zKkn8vre0f8rVT?utm_source=generator" width="100%" height="152" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="w-1/2 p-4">
        <iframe style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/3p2DDJagrr1sgncalMBS1d?utm_source=generator" width="100%" height="152" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-lg text-primary-300 md:text-primary-100">
      <Trans i18nKey="about.body22">
        I have been playing guitar since I was little, and when I was younger I wrote a few songs.
        <br />
        <br />
        Here's one I recorded many years ago, check it out!
      </Trans>
    </p>
    <iframe width="50%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/59032090&color=%23ff5500&auto_play=false&hide_related=false&show_comments=true&show_user=true&show_reposts=false&show_teaser=true" loading="lazy"></iframe><div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc;line-break: anywhere;word-break: normal;overflow: hidden;white-space: nowrap;text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif;font-weight: 100;"><a href="https://soundcloud.com/etc2702" title="etc2702" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;">etc2702</a> Â· <a href="https://soundcloud.com/etc2702/julianne" title="Julianne" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;">Julianne</a></div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-7xl lg:px-8 lg:bg-transparent bg-contentbackground"
  >
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12">
      <div
        class="z-10 lg:col-span-4 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-1 lg:py-16 lg:bg-transparent"
      >
        <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-xs sm:px-6 md:max-w-md lg:p-0">
          <img
            decoding="async"
            loading="lazy"
            class="object-cover object-center w-full max-w-md rounded-3xl shadow-2xl rotate-2 aspect-[1/1]"
            src="/images/kiwi.webp"
            alt={t("about.img3")}
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative rounded-3xl lg:grid lg:grid-cols-10 lg:col-span-10 lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-1 lg:items-center lg:bg-contentbackground"
      >
        <div
          class="hidden overflow-hidden absolute inset-0 rounded-3xl pointer-events-none lg:block"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <svg
            class="absolute bottom-full left-full opacity-20 transform -translate-x-2/3 translate-y-1/3 xl:top-0 xl:bottom-auto xl:translate-y-0"
            width="404"
            height="384"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 404 384"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <defs>
              <pattern
                id="64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
              >
                <rect
                  x="0"
                  y="0"
                  width="4"
                  height="4"
                  class="text-accent-500"
                  fill="currentColor"></rect>
              </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect
              width="404"
              height="384"
              fill="url(#64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d)"></rect>
          </svg>
          <svg
            class="absolute top-full opacity-40 transform -translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/3 xl:-translate-y-1/2"
            width="404"
            height="384"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 404 384"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <defs>
              <pattern
                id="64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
              >
                <rect
                  x="0"
                  y="0"
                  width="4"
                  height="4"
                  class="text-accent-500"
                  fill="currentColor"></rect>
              </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect
              width="404"
              height="384"
              fill="url(#64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d)"></rect>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div
          class="py-4 mx-auto space-y-6 sm:py-8 sm:max-w-3xl lg:col-span-7 lg:col-start-4 lg:max-w-none"
        >
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl"
            id="about-heading"
          >
          <Trans i18nKey="about.heading3">
            Me and my partner have a little Dachshund. His name is <strong>Kiwi</strong>.
          </Trans>
        </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-primary-300 md:text-primary-100 text-justify">
            {t("about.body3")} &#128163;
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
